task.summary: Removed unused gulp imports. Changed package.json
Added people to assign todo's to. Added a field to tell if a todo is a subtask of another todo Added d3 visualization of the tasks assigned to Patrick van Vuuren (Future: Switch persons)
Added the possibility to switch between persons, to show their own todo's and subtasks. Also did some refactoring.

Refactored refs, now using componentWillReceiveProps to update child components according to the parent's state.
Restyled the page for a bigger visualization container

Removed browserify build, switched to webpack for react hot loader and automatic bundling.
TODO: Convert jasmine tests to jest tests, and specify them under a __tests__ directory in the component's directory.
Added gulpfile for testing with Jasmine and it's dependencies, jest is does not work in node 0.11/0.12.
